Interface ChangeLogManager


  • public interface ChangeLogManager
    Defines the capabilities of a class which can be used to manage persistently backed change log objects.

                  java.lang.String bucketName,

        Create a change log with the supplied data.
        Parameters:
        trackedMoFdn - FDN of tracked managed object
        namespace - namespace of tracked object
        type - type of tracked object
        operationName - name of operation being tracked
        additionalData - additional data relevant for the operation being tracked. May be null if no additional data needs to be stored.
        originalAttributes - original properties on managed object if relevant, may be null if no attributes are relevant to the operation being created.
        suppliedArguments - arguments supplied for the operation, may be null.
        bucketName - the name of the data bucket containing the tracked managed object
        username - currently logged user username value
